.com/hkdogrescue/</a><br />\n👆🏻Hong Kong Dog Rescue (HKDR) 嘅鴨脷洲中心有好多小型犬，有興趣嘅話樓主可以預約探訪<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/KirstensZooCharity/photos/a.134824390199117/1212839675730911/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FKirstensZooCharity%2Fphotos%2Fa.134824390199117%2F1212839675730911%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCIR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=89a1035d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/KirstensZooCharity/photos/a.134824390199117/1212839675730911/?type=3</a><br />\n👆🏻Kirsten's Zoo Charity 嘅細身唐狗，佢地仲有另外一隻松鼠狗待領養<br />\n<br />\n希望樓主選擇支持領養，唔好助長繁殖場🙏🏻"}]}